{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban music venues from stopping solo people visiting",
        "additional_details": "I think this is discrimination at its finest. People on their own are no different to the next person going into a venue. Being solo or in a group shouldn\u2019t matter. It shouldn\u2019t be allowed that solo visitors are refused entry purely based on the fact they're on their own.\r\n \r\nI chose to go out on my own. I feel like I have been victimised on the basis of being solo.",
        "background": "I want the government to stop venues refusing entry purely based on the person being alone. I recently visited Manchester to attend a gig and several venues refused entry due to being on my own.",
